   A health care workforce that is up to the challenges of the new
   century--that has the capacity to serve an increasingly divers
   population and to deliver quality care in underserved areas--is the
   cornerstone on which health care access is built. HRSA is helping
   eliminate heatlh disparities, supporing more than 40 programs to
   increase racial and ethnic represntation within the health care
   industry and improve the geographic distribution of health care
   professionals in underserved areas. You have selected 0 items to be
   ordered.





